      <t>Lawful Intercept stands for legally authorized capture &amp; delivery of
   subscriber communications data by a communications provider to a law
   enforcement agency.This document describes Generic Lawful Intercept
   Architecture Models &amp; implementation considerations for Service
   Provider Wi-Fi deployments.</t>
